highlights.text: “Sweater Weather” by The Neighbourhood has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 1830 days straight.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Tears” is the highest at #2.
“DOG HOUSE (feat. Julia Wolf & Yeat)” by Drake, Julia Wolf, and Yeat is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #73.
“Romantic Homicide” by d4vd is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 71 spots at #113.
